{"tid":1875729,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔墟站沙田圍站現可疑鞋盒　警引爆內藏石頭紙條","createTime":"2020-02-12T03:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T04:36:36.000Z","uid":241764,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2140895ed0cc3d0ac2801b4054b8a02ef5d24fb8","tid":1875729,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"港鐵發生兩宗懷疑發現炸彈案件，警方先後於大埔墟站及沙田圍站引爆兩個可疑紙盒，均為「詐彈」，正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n首宗案件發生於凌晨4時許，港鐵職員於大埔墟站與太和站之間檢查路軌期間，發現中段路軌上有一個可疑鞋盒，於是報警。警方到場觀察後懷疑該鞋盒內藏爆炸品，急召爆炸品處理課（EOD）及消防到場跟進，曾封鎖附近一帶北盛街及太和橋。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸品處理課派出拆彈機械人，早上6時許引爆可疑鞋盒，盒內僅有一塊拳頭般大小石頭，並無爆炸品。港鐵近7時確認安全，東鐵線服務回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n另一宗案件發生於清晨6時許，有人於馬鞍山線沙田圍站對開行人路發現一個可疑鞋盒，警方懷疑該鞋盒內藏爆炸品，再急召爆炸品處理課及消防到場跟進，並曾封鎖沙田圍站對開整條沙角街。<br />\n<br />\n爆炸品處理課再派出拆彈機械人，兩度引爆可疑鞋盒，內有數枚電池及一套相信是照明系統用的火牛，並有一張寫有「港警暴」紙條。<br />\n<br />\n兩宗案件均無人受傷，警員檢走兩個鞋盒碎片跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200212/s00001/1581473295007/%e5%a4%a7%e5%9f%94%e5%a2%9f%e7%ab%99%e6%b2%99%e7%94%b0%e5%9c%8d%e7%ab%99%e7%8f%be%e5%8f%af%e7%96%91%e9%9e%8b%e7%9b%92-%e8%ad%a6%e5%bc%95%e7%88%86%e5%85%a7%e8%97%8f%e7%9f%b3%e9%a0%ad%e7%b4%99%e6%a2%9d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200212%2Fs00001%2F1581473295007%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%259f%2594%25e5%25a2%259f%25e7%25ab%2599%25e6%25b2%2599%25e7%2594%25b0%25e5%259c%258d%25e7%25ab%2599%25e7%258f%25be%25e5%258f%25af%25e7%2596%2591%25e9%259e%258b%25e7%259b%2592-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25bc%2595%25e7%2588%2586%25e5%2585%25a7%25e8%2597%258f%25e7%259f%25b3%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e7%25b4%2599%25e6%25a2%259d&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BR4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=25407c34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200212%2Fs00001%2F1581473295007%2F%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%259f%2594%25e5%25a2%259f%25e7%25ab%2599%25e6%25b2%2599%25e7%2594%25b0%25e5%259c%258d%25e7%25ab%2599%25e7%258f%25be%25e5%258f%25af%25e7%2596%2591%25e9%259e%258b%25e7%259b%2592-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%25bc%2595%25e7%2588%2586%25e5%2585%25a7%25e8%2597%258f%25e7%259f%25b3%25e9%25a0%25ad%25e7%25b4%2599%25e6%25a2%259d&h=44a2474d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200212/s00001/1581473295007/%e5%a4%a7%e5%9f%94%e5%a2%9f%e7%ab%99%e6%b2%99%e7%94%b0%e5%9c%8d%e7%ab%99%e7%8f%be%e5%8f%af%e7%96%91%e9%9e%8b%e7%9b%92-%e8%ad%a6%e5%bc%95%e7%88%86%e5%85%a7%e8%97%8f%e7%9f%b3%e9%a0%ad%e7%b4%99%e6%a2%9d</a><br />\n<br />\n點解唔係口罩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2546129bdbf8a7d40346c16e3c57215ddc561796","tid":1875729,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81da9429db1a5cf6470b7d5d46891abbd5759cc9","tid":1875729,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:51:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a6b6ed154da555da64fc114adc34f319b40ca5e","tid":1875729,"uid":44562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T03:51:42.000Z","msg":"放置(空)鞋盒師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ff7ad193d032145845d986ac911a0c55e6a58b","tid":1875729,"uid":195887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:35:47.000Z","msg":"如果真係唔記得左拎走d火牛，咁你班仆街同我炸撚左佢。 有無得叫黑警賠？"},{"pid":"bc35efa773d9657d43116df89c793bd8a44b364e","tid":1875729,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"甘大滋啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}